    "Figure 13 illustrated confusion matrix the exceptional classification performance of the PolynetDWTCADx framework across 24 classes.",
    "The high values along the diagonal demonstrate the model's robustness, accurately predicting the preponderance of samples for each class.",
    "As an illustration, the model demonstrated exceptional precision in Class 4 (595 accurately forecasted samples), Class 13 (660 correct predictions), and Class 14 (538 correct predictions).",
    "The model effectively captures the underlying features for classes with complex patterns, such as Class 6 and Class 8, as demonstrated by the strong classification numbers (560 and 46, respectively).",
    "These results underscore the model's capacity to manage diverse and challenging classes with high precision, ensuring dependable predictions for critical clinical applications."
